{
  "texts": [
    "ConclusionOverall, this systematic review provides important information on the benefits of using chatbots in medical history taking.",
    "They improve patient engagement by increasing data completeness and user satisfaction.",
    "They capture accurate and comprehensive patient data, which is crucial for diagnosis.",
    "In addition, chatbots can increase efficiency by significantly reducing data collection time.",
    "For example, chatbots can be used in primary care to record a patient's medical history before a consultation."
  ]
}